summary: A small dungeon across from Riverwood.
descriptionHtml:
[center][img]http://static-3.nexusmods.com/15/mods/110/images/56611-2-1407269247.jpg[/img]ï»¿[/center]

This is a small dungeon I created while going through the creation kit tutorials. It has no associated quests but the endboss carries a unique mask. The enchantment on the mask, covered by the flavor text, is 20% fortify shout, 50% fortify health regeneration, 20% fortify magic resistance. Due to some pathing mistakes, enemies will come at you like you've stolen their sweetroll. It is doable but probably not with a naked lvl1 character.

This requires both Dawnguard and Dragonborn.
author: Miaxi
